{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "main_14", "eventName": "慈悲燈塔", "entryType": "MAINLINE", "storyCode": "14-5", "avgTag": "行動前", "storyName": "探查岩洞區域", "storyInfo": "W、赫德雷等人在防守墜落的“生命脊椎”，W手下的佣兵卻在陌生的環境中失踪。找回隊友的過程中，W等人遭到了詭異怪物的襲擊。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_towerinside", "screenadapt": "showall"}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$darkness01_intro", "key": "$darkness01_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "倫蒂尼姆外圍地塊，荒廢的宅邸"}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_399_1#1$1", "duration": 0.7}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_399_1#1$1", "duration": 0.7}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_399_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她回來了嗎？", "name": "緊張的私兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_399_1#1$1"}, {"id": 17, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_399_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還沒有。", "name": "不滿的私兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_399_1#1$1"}, {"id": 19, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_399_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "真該死！能躲開那些魔族佬就已經夠不容易的了，怎麼她不僅沒死，還能找到我們——", "name": "緊張的私兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_399_1#1$1"}, {"id": 21, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她是怎麼知道，我之前和那些魔族佬做過生意的？", "name": "緊張的私兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_399_1#1$1"}, {"id": 22, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_399_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈，反正那些魔族佬現在也不管你了。", "name": "不滿的私兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_399_1#1$1"}, {"id": 24, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_399_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你呢，你是怎麼落到她手上的？", "name": "緊張的私兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_399_1#1$1"}, {"id": 26, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_399_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……她用弩頂著我的腦袋。", "name": "不滿的私兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_399_1#1$1"}, {"id": 28, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我以前就認識她，她那個時候可沒這麼——", "name": "不滿的私兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_399_1#1$1"}, {"id": 29, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "musicvolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.3, "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$e_atk_arrowload_n", "volume": 0.7}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒這麼，什麼？", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1342_1#1$1", "bstart": 0.2, "bend": 0.7, "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "musicvolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.6, "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1342_1#1$1", "bstart": 0.2, "bend": 0.7, "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "說下去。", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1342_1#1$1"}, {"id": 41, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_399_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊，不，我沒有——", "name": "不滿的私兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_399_1#1$1"}, {"id": 43, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_chairbump", "volume": 0.7}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$bodyfalldown1", "volume": 1.0, "delay": 0.2}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0, "xstrength": 25.0, "ystrength": 35.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "為公爵們幹了一輩子工作的私兵癱倒在地，一把弩支在他的額頭上，閃著寒光的箭尖抵著他的腦袋。"}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "來人的聲音冷漠如冰。"}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1342_1#1$1", "bstart": 0.2, "bend": 0.7, "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "說下去。", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1342_1#1$1"}, {"id": 53, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我只是——對、對不起，“銑痕”小姐！", "name": "恐懼的私兵"}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "恐懼的私兵", "content": "我、我不該——"}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_arrowtarget", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "恐懼的私兵", "content": "啊！！！"}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "弩箭洞穿了他的耳廓。"}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1342_1#1$1", "bstart": 0.2, "bend": 0.7, "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1342_1#1$1", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "200,0", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1342_1#1$1", "bstart": 0.0, "bend": 0.0, "duration": 2.0, "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1342_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有的人會給自己寵物的耳朵上打孔，來證明它的歸屬。", "name": "“銑痕”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1342_1#1$1"}, {"id": 72, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當然，人不是寵物。但……某些方面也都一樣，對吧？", "name": "“銑痕”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1342_1#1$1"}, {"id": 73, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我……", "name": "恐懼的私兵"}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1342_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "現在，爬起來，給我一個結論。", "name": "“銑痕”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1342_1#6$1"}, {"id": 78, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我讓你們幹的事情怎麼樣了？", "name": "“銑痕”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1342_1#6$1"}, {"id": 79, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.2}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_clothmovementsp", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "xstrength": 20.0, "ystrength": 20.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_399_1#1$1", "duration": 0.7}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好、好的，“銑痕”小姐！", "name": "恐懼的私兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_399_1#1$1"}, {"id": 87, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們盡可能匯總了情報。監聽站的訊號很差，我們只能竭盡所能——", "name": "恐懼的私兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_399_1#1$1"}, {"id": 88, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1342_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我只要結論。", "name": "“銑痕”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1342_1#6$1"}, {"id": 90, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_399_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "從“灰禮帽”殘留的訊息，和偶爾能攔截到的通訊來看，確實有一支叫“典範軍”的隊伍成立了，領導人很可能就是您說的那位……", "name": "恐懼的私兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_399_1#1$1"}, {"id": 92, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“維娜”小姐。", "name": "恐懼的私兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_399_1#1$1"}, {"id": 93, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們似乎正在前往……銀石崖前線。", "name": "恐懼的私兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_399_1#1$1"}, {"id": 94, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1342_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……銀石崖。他們居然還真的留在了戰場上。", "name": "“銑痕”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1342_1#7$1"}, {"id": 96, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1342_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "繼續。有什麼新的資訊隨時通知我。", "name": "“銑痕”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1342_1#1$1"}, {"id": 98, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_399_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好、好的！", "name": "恐懼的私兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_399_1#1$1"}, {"id": 100, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_black", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_runstop", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1342_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——呼。", "name": "“銑痕”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1342_1#2$1"}, {"id": 111, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1342_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呵，其實幹這些事，比我原本預想的要輕鬆。", "name": "“銑痕”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1342_1#8$1"}, {"id": 113, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我原以為，我會有更多負擔呢。", "name": "“銑痕”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1342_1#8$1"}, {"id": 114, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不用顧忌什麼，也不用扮演什麼。", "name": "“銑痕”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1342_1#8$1"}, {"id": 115, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1342_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我找到“維多利亞”了。", "name": "“銑痕”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1342_1#9$1"}, {"id": 117, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_steamrelease"}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {"name": "$eb_glow_l", "layer": 1.0, "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "濃重的陰影中，一道赤紅的光芒閃爍了幾下。"}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你的職責，不就是守護她嗎？", "name": "“銑痕”"}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_black", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$ponder_intro", "key": "$ponder_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "行動開始後四十三小時"}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "43_g2_giantmonsterspine", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1067_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我就知道，你還是會來的。", "name": "厄爾蘇拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1067_1#1$1"}, {"id": 148, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4088_hodrer_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4088_hodrer_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……厄爾蘇拉。", "name": "赫德雷"}, "figure_art": "avg_4088_hodrer_1#1$1"}, {"id": 155, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_ironchaindrop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1067_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "過去幾十個小時裡，那個喜歡玩炸彈的W來過一次，為我精心打造了這個監獄。", "name": "厄爾蘇拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1067_1#5$1"}, {"id": 160, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "伊內絲來過兩次，表達了一下對我的“關懷”。她還是老樣子，一旦注意力放在別人影子上，嗆人的時候反應就會慢一拍。", "name": "厄爾蘇拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1067_1#5$1"}, {"id": 161, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "現在輪到你了？又想來說什麼？", "name": "厄爾蘇拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1067_1#5$1"}, {"id": 162, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4088_hodrer_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你考慮好了嗎？", "name": "赫德雷"}, "figure_art": "avg_4088_hodrer_1#1$1"}, {"id": 164, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1067_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這個問題應該我問你。", "name": "厄爾蘇拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1067_1#1$1"}, {"id": 166, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們的處境岌岌可危，唯一能指望的載具癱瘓在這。", "name": "厄爾蘇拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1067_1#1$1"}, {"id": 167, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而我作為駕駛員，很可能掌握著什麼你們不知道的秘密，說不準什麼時候就會偷襲你們一次。", "name": "厄爾蘇拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1067_1#1$1"}, {"id": 168, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "赫德雷，你真的應該殺了我。", "name": "厄爾蘇拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1067_1#1$1"}, {"id": 169, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4088_hodrer_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我更希望你能用你知道的情報來幫我們。", "name": "赫德雷"}, "figure_art": "avg_4088_hodrer_1#1$1"}, {"id": 171, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1067_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別說夢話。", "name": "厄爾蘇拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1067_1#5$1"}, {"id": 173, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我早就拒絕過你，你要是覺得我被你們俘虜就能改變立場，那你就太瞧不起我了。", "name": "厄爾蘇拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1067_1#5$1"}, {"id": 174, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4088_hodrer_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……三條命。", "name": "赫德雷"}, "figure_art": "avg_4088_hodrer_1#8$1"}, {"id": 176, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1067_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯？", "name": "厄爾蘇拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1067_1#10$1"}, {"id": 178, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4088_hodrer_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在卡茲戴爾的時候，你救過我們三次。我一次，伊內絲兩次。", "name": "赫德雷"}, "figure_art": "avg_4088_hodrer_1#2$1"}, {"id": 180, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1067_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這都是你在日記本上記的？", "name": "厄爾蘇拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1067_1#10$1"}, {"id": 182, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4088_hodrer_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "算個價吧，我想辦法還給你。", "name": "赫德雷"}, "figure_art": "avg_4088_hodrer_1#1$1"}, {"id": 184, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1067_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "赫德雷，你就算不當雇傭兵回卡茲戴爾開家小店，也會賠到血本無歸的。", "name": "厄爾蘇拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1067_1#8$1"}, {"id": 186, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4088_hodrer_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我只是希望，能活著回到卡茲戴爾的薩卡茲，盡可能多一點。", "name": "赫德雷"}, "figure_art": "avg_4088_hodrer_1#1$1"}, {"id": 188, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1067_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "真宏大。", "name": "厄爾蘇拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1067_1#8$1"}, {"id": 190, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1067_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好了，事到如今，疤痕商場的老規矩，就把它丟在卡茲戴爾地底吧。我們之間的帳，一筆勾銷。", "name": "厄爾蘇拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1067_1#1$1"}, {"id": 192, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "最後一次勸誡，赫德雷。現在不殺我的話，你一定會後悔的。", "name": "厄爾蘇拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1067_1#1$1"}, {"id": 193, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4088_hodrer_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "厄爾蘇拉，你有沒有想過，我們的目標從來都是一致的——", "name": "赫德雷"}, "figure_art": "avg_4088_hodrer_1#1$1"}, {"id": 195, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1067_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別說了。你那些正確的理論我都聽膩了。", "name": "厄爾蘇拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1067_1#2$1"}, {"id": 197, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1067_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別想用漂亮話買我的命，老朋友。這沒比錢強上多少。", "name": "厄爾蘇拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1067_1#1$1"}, {"id": 199, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "雇傭兵是沒有立場……但你和我，早就不只是雇傭兵了。", "name": "厄爾蘇拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1067_1#1$1"}, {"id": 200, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "43_g1_giantmonstercockpit", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_412_1#10$1", "duration": 0.7}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4087_ines_1#1$1", "duration": 0.7}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_412_1#10$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "伊內絲，打個賭嗎？", "name": "W"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_412_1#10$1"}, {"id": 213, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "赫德雷會和厄爾蘇拉聊聊過去疤痕商場的情誼，厄爾蘇拉要求他盡快動手，然後過不了多久赫德雷就會一臉惆悵地回來。", "name": "W"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_412_1#10$1"}, {"id": 214, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4087_ines_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你要賭什麼？", "name": "伊內絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4087_ines_1#1$1"}, {"id": 216, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_412_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你就這個反應？我還以為放他們兩個單獨相處，你會狠狠吃醋來著。", "name": "W"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_412_1#1$1"}, {"id": 218, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4087_ines_1#9$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……W。", "name": "伊內絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4087_ines_1#9$1"}, {"id": 220, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_412_1#3$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別再盯著我的影子反覆欣賞了，伊內絲，煩死了。", "name": "W"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_412_1#3$1"}, {"id": 222, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "小兔子和維多利亞人走了好久了吧……也不知道他們那邊怎麼樣了。", "name": "W"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_412_1#3$1"}, {"id": 223, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這骨頭架子還在裝死，特雷西斯搞出來的浮誇天災又陰魂不散，也不知道曼弗雷德是不是下一秒就會蹦出來。", "name": "W"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_412_1#3$1"}, {"id": 224, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_412_1#6$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊……本來炸死特雷西斯的機會都近在眼前了！", "name": "W"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_412_1#6$1"}, {"id": 226, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4087_ines_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "W，我知道你還在因為特蕾西婭的事躁動。可你最好確保你的炸彈腦袋冷靜下來，我們現在要準備的事還有很多。", "name": "伊內絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4087_ines_1#1$1"}, {"id": 228, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_412_1#11$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 25.0, "ystrength": 25.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "*薩卡茲粗口*！誰說我——", "name": "W"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_412_1#11$1"}, {"id": 231, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral", "volume": 0.9}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1336_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$nervous_intro", "key": "$nervous_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1336_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "W，有些狀況……", "name": "W小隊成員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1336_1#1$1"}, {"id": 240, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_412_1#13$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "說。", "name": "W"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_412_1#13$1"}, {"id": 242, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1336_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "到了換班的時候，我們派出去偵察的人，有些沒回來。", "name": "W小隊成員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1336_1#1$1"}, {"id": 244, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“吊塔”那一隊，十個人去峽谷北邊了。現在聯繫不上。", "name": "W小隊成員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1336_1#1$1"}, {"id": 245, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_412_1#13$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "難道是遇到能幹的術師了？", "name": "W"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_412_1#13$1"}, {"id": 247, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4087_ines_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 248, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們最後一次聯絡是在什麼時候？", "name": "伊內絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4087_ines_1#9$1"}, {"id": 249, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1336_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 250, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "差不多三個小時前。", "name": "W小隊成員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1336_1#1$1"}, {"id": 251, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4087_ines_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 252, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果敵人能讓一整支傭兵隊伍悄無聲息地消失，他們這會應該已經打過來了。", "name": "伊內絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4087_ines_1#10$1"}, {"id": 253, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4087_ines_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 254, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "W，現在最重要的任務還是守好脊椎，不要輕舉妄動。", "name": "伊內絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4087_ines_1#9$1"}, {"id": 255, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_412_1#13$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 256, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "外面有狀況，我們就這麼坐在這乾等？", "name": "W"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_412_1#13$1"}, {"id": 257, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4132_ascln_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 258, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我同意伊內絲的想法。", "name": "阿斯卡綸"}, "figure_art": "avg_4132_ascln_1#1$1"}, {"id": 259, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們對外面戰場的情況一無所知，最穩妥的戰術是集中力量防守一處。", "name": "阿斯卡綸"}, "figure_art": "avg_4132_ascln_1#1$1"}, {"id": 260, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_412_1#11$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒那麼多廢話，我的人平白無故地消失了，總要有個理由。", "name": "W"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_412_1#11$1"}, {"id": 262, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "要是迷路了就帶他們回來，要是遇見敵人就提前幹掉。", "name": "W"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_412_1#11$1"}, {"id": 263, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4087_ines_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 264, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "冷靜點！萬一是敵人分散我們戰鬥力的陷阱——", "name": "伊內絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4087_ines_1#9$1"}, {"id": 265, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_412_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 266, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我討厭陷入被動……我主動出擊，就算是陷阱，也可以先用炸彈炸得他們現身。", "name": "W"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_412_1#5$1"}, {"id": 267, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "給我半天時間，要是我沒回來，那就一定是遇到了難對付的傢伙，其他人不要再追過來，全力防守。", "name": "W"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_412_1#5$1"}, {"id": 268, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "要是期間收到了阿米婭的通訊，也不用管我，你們立即啟動脊椎。", "name": "W"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_412_1#5$1"}, {"id": 269, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_412_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 270, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不耽誤其他人工夫，我自己帶隊過去。", "name": "W"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_412_1#8$1"}, {"id": 271, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們幾個，帶好傢伙，我們走。", "name": "W"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_412_1#8$1"}, {"id": 272, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 274, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 275, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 276, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 277, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "50_g18_originiumcave", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 278, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 279, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$formal_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 280, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 281, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_bodyfallvalley", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 282, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_cloakmovement", "volume": 1.0, "delay": 2.0}}, {"id": 283, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 2.0, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 284, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 285, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1336_1#1$1", "duration": 0.7}}, {"id": 286, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_412_1#13$1", "duration": 0.7}}, {"id": 287, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 288, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_412_1#13$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 289, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們來的就是這個地方？", "name": "W"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_412_1#13$1"}, {"id": 290, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1336_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 291, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "按理說就是這個方向，我們往峽谷北邊深處走，只看到有這個山洞，不知道裡面是什麼。", "name": "W小隊成員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1336_1#1$1"}, {"id": 292, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "也許是條密道？這裡會不會是什麼王庭軍藏寶貝的秘密據點？", "name": "W小隊成員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1336_1#1$1"}, {"id": 293, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_412_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 294, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這裡要真的是王庭軍的秘密基地，我們掉下來的第一時間就會有兩百個血魔和食腐者圍過來唱咒術歌。", "name": "W"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_412_1#1$1"}, {"id": 295, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "按之前可露希爾給的資訊，我們大概是在倫蒂尼姆西邊的荒山裡，離老傢伙們的正面戰場還遠得很呢。", "name": "W"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_412_1#1$1"}, {"id": 296, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_412_1#6$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 297, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "W", "content": "但是話說回來，總覺得有一股……（嗅聞）……"}}, {"id": 298, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_412_1#8$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 299, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "W", "content": "有人待過的老舊到發霉的味道。"}}, {"id": 300, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我討厭古老的東西，但赫德雷一定會喜歡。", "name": "W"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_412_1#8$1"}, {"id": 301, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 302, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_sandstone", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 303, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 304, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_412_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 305, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "讓我猜猜看，我們的這些幸運兒是碰上了什麼敵人？", "name": "W"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_412_1#1$1"}, {"id": 306, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1336_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 307, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "W，你什麼時候用炸彈了？", "name": "W小隊成員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1336_1#1$1"}, {"id": 308, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_412_1#13$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 309, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "胡說些什麼？我們一路過來什麼時候用炸彈了？", "name": "W"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_412_1#13$1"}, {"id": 310, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1336_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 311, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "牆壁上這些灼痕……？", "name": "W小隊成員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1336_1#1$1"}, {"id": 312, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_412_1#12$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 313, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊……？", "name": "W"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_412_1#12$1"}, {"id": 314, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "奇怪，能把石頭燒成這樣，但又沒有法術的痕跡？這是在做什麼……", "name": "W"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_412_1#12$1"}, {"id": 315, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1336_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 316, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 15.0, "ystrength": 15.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 317, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "聽到了嗎？！", "name": "W小隊成員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1336_1#1$1"}, {"id": 318, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_412_1#12$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 319, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一驚一乍幹什麼？", "name": "W"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_412_1#12$1"}, {"id": 320, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1336_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 321, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "打鐵……我聽到了有人在打鐵——這裡有人！", "name": "W小隊成員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1336_1#1$1"}, {"id": 322, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 323, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_412_1#12$1", "focus": "all"}}, {"id": 324, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 325, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_412_1#13$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 326, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "胡說些什麼……", "name": "W"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_412_1#13$1"}, {"id": 327, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "少在那嚇唬自己，這裡明明半個人影都沒有。", "name": "W"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_412_1#13$1"}, {"id": 328, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1336_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 329, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "W……我們還要往裡面走嗎？我感覺有點不太對勁。", "name": "W小隊成員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1336_1#1$1"}, {"id": 330, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_412_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 331, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "廢話，我們出來是幹什麼的。", "name": "W"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_412_1#1$1"}, {"id": 332, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "跟著我的那些小弟小妹們身上用的都是上等貨，我還沒富裕到眼睜睜看著那些裝備爛在地下。", "name": "W"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_412_1#1$1"}, {"id": 333, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1336_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 334, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你有沒有聽說過一個薩卡茲的傳說……在奎隆都還沒有出生的時候，薩卡茲曾經跟紅龍——", "name": "W小隊成員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1336_1#1$1"}, {"id": 335, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_412_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 336, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "閉嘴。", "name": "W"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_412_1#1$1"}, {"id": 337, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "上歷史課的有赫德雷一個就夠了，再多說一句，我就先把你扔到前面——", "name": "W"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_412_1#1$1"}, {"id": 338, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 339, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_412_1#5$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 340, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——！", "name": "W"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_412_1#5$1"}, {"id": 341, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1336_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 342, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "怎麼了……？", "name": "W小隊成員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1336_1#1$1"}, {"id": 343, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_412_1#5$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 344, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有股血的味道……但不是薩卡茲的血。", "name": "W"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_412_1#5$1"}, {"id": 345, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "W", "content": "是不久前才留下的——"}}, {"id": 346, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$plot_intro", "key": "$plot_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 347, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_412_1#11$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 348, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 349, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "W", "content": "戒備！"}}, {"id": 350, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 351, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 352, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_land_impact", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 353, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_rockfall", "volume": 0.6, "delay": 0.2}}, {"id": 354, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_land_impact", "volume": 0.6, "loop": "false", "channel": "cmr", "delay": 0.7}}, {"id": 355, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 2.0, "xstrength": 40.0, "ystrength": 40.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 356, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 357, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_chimera", "volume": 0.8}}, {"id": 358, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1335_1#1$1", "bstart": 0.5, "bend": 0.9, "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 359, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 2.5, "xstrength": 40.0, "ystrength": 40.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 360, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.0}}, {"id": 361, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "吼————————！", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1335_1#1$1"}, {"id": 362, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 363, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 364, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 365, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 366, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 367, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}